Page_0:
"Dear Ms. Jennings,

I'll be in the watch tower tonite and keep an eye on yer museum office's window. When ye give me the signal, I'll unlock the backdoor and send the other watchmen of me shift outside for a break, so ye can come in unseen. Most likely it'll take me a while to get rid of 'em all - especially Jorek can be a stubborn oaf when he's at the equipment store - so please give me a moment or two.
The entrance to the war tunnel is in the last cell. Look for a small switch above eye level at the back of the stone arch next to the cell.

Ned
P.S.: I burned your note during my outside patrol, like you told me to."
